Masa natal ketika kita kembali ke Leoch.

233
00:16:37,326 --> 00:16:39,036
Natal...

234
00:16:39,036 --> 00:16:42,331
Kurasa tak perlu mengenakan stocking.

235
00:16:42,331 --> 00:16:44,499
Maksudmu mencoba mengeringkannya?

236
00:16:44,499 --> 00:16:46,835
Tak usah dipikirkan.

237
00:16:46,835 --> 00:16:52,131
<i>Kalau begitu istrinya penjaga kuda bisa jadi hangat,</i>

238
