276
00:19:57,760 --> 00:19:59,720
Kurasa aku tepat waktu.

277
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,513
Aku kira kau datang lebih awal.

278
00:20:13,149 --> 00:20:14,900
Ini.

279
00:20:20,114 --> 00:20:21,156
Di mana?

280
00:20:25,243 --> 00:20:26,411
Berikan kami uangnya.

281
00:20:43,093 --> 00:20:44,761
Hentikan!

282
00:20:44,761 --> 00:20:46,346
Kumohon hentikan!

283
