357
00:24:51,612 --> 00:24:54,490
Jadi... tepat di sana?

358
00:24:54,490 --> 00:24:55,991
Whoa, jangan membunuhnya dulu, nyonya.

359
00:24:55,991 --> 00:24:57,952
Tunggu sampai pelajaran usai.

360
00:25:00,287 --> 00:25:04,541
Willie, tolong kami.

361
00:25:04,541 --> 00:25:06,418
Berbaliklah, supaya aku bisa menunjukkan
