444
00:31:42,489 --> 00:31:44,991
di mana kekuatan alam bersatu.

445
00:31:44,991 --> 00:31:47,369
Segala macam takhayul.

446
00:31:50,496 --> 00:31:52,582
Lanjutkan.

447
00:31:52,582 --> 00:31:54,625
Bebatuan itu mengandung kekuatan,

448
00:31:54,625 --> 00:31:59,421
<i>dan memberi fokus, seperti kaca, kau tahu?</i>

449
00:31:59,421 --> 00:32:02,049
Dan untuk beberapa orang,

450
00:32:02,049 --> 00:32:05,302
